{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_02_02",
  "title": "白石千紗",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さ～ん、助けて下さい～",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ、千紗。何かあったのか？",
      "startTime": 5.166666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "例のユニットのメンバー四人で\n初めてレッスンをしたんですけど……",
      "startTime": 11.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "初回だから一人ずつ自己紹介することになって\n私は遙子さんの真似をして名前と年齢を言ったんです",
      "startTime": 19.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "白石千紗、十七歳です、って……\nそしたらこころちゃんに怒られちゃって……",
      "startTime": 29.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "こころとキャラがかぶるので止めて下さい\nって言われました……",
      "startTime": 35.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばこころはいつも言ってるな\nみんなのこころを鷲掴み、赤崎こころ十四歳です、って",
      "startTime": 41.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "それで私、あたふたしちゃって\nそこからはうまく喋れなかったんです",
      "startTime": 51.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "最年長の私がみんなを引っ張らなきゃいけないのに……",
      "startTime": 54.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それで初レッスンはどうなったんだ？",
      "startTime": 60.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃんが仕切ったり提案したりしてくれて\nレッスンは無事に終わりました",
      "startTime": 67.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "最初はみんなぎこちなかったけど\nこころちゃんのトークで和んで明るくなったんです",
      "startTime": 72.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "私はこころちゃんみたいに出来なかったんです\n私の方がお姉さんなのに……",
      "startTime": 82.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "それで、このままじゃいけないと思って\n思い切ってこころちゃんに聞いてみたんです",
      "startTime": 88.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "私はみんなのお姉さんになりたいんだけど\nどうしたらいいのかなって",
      "startTime": 94.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "年下のこころにそれを聞いたのか……",
      "startTime": 97.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "そしたらこころちゃんが教えてくれたんです\n腹筋を毎日千回やればみんなついてきてくれるよって",
      "startTime": 104.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "それで昨日は一人でずっと腹筋をしてたんですけど\nお腹が筋肉痛になっちゃって……",
      "startTime": 114.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "こころの言うことは鵜呑みにしない方がいいと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 117.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "でもこころちゃんは本当に凄いんです\nムードメーカーで、存在感があって、いつも前向きで",
      "startTime": 125.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "レッスン中もこころちゃんが盛り上げて\n私達を引っ張ってくれたんです",
      "startTime": 133.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "あたふたして何も出来なかった私とは大違いです……",
      "startTime": 135.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "まだ一回目のレッスンだ。そこまで考えなくても……\n千紗はこれから頑張ればいいんだよ",
      "startTime": 145.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "でも、どれだけ私が頑張っても\n年上らしく振る舞えるかどうか……",
      "startTime": 152.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "きっと出来るさ\n千紗はもっと自分に自信を持っていいと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 157.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "自分に自信……そうですよね\n私でもみんなのお姉さんになれますよね",
      "startTime": 165.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "いくらこころちゃんが凄いからって\n全部任せきりはダメですよね",
      "startTime": 173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "最年長の私がもっとしっかりしないと……",
      "startTime": 176.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんの真似をして失敗したので\n次はお姉ちゃんを参考にしてみます",
      "startTime": 184.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "私がみんなのお姉さんになれるように\nもう少し頑張ってみます！",
      "startTime": 190.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 193.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 194.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 194.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりダメでした……",
      "startTime": 195.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "心が折れるのが早いな……。今度は何があったんだ？",
      "startTime": 198.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs025.m4a",
      "text": "あれから何度か四人でレッスンしたんですけど\n前向きなすずちゃんが積極的に動いて",
      "startTime": 207.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "しっかり者のすみれちゃんがフォローして\n明るくて元気なこころちゃんが盛り上げて……",
      "startTime": 214.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 218.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs027.m4a",
      "text": "私がいなくてもみんなちゃんと出来ていて\n私の出る幕がないんです……",
      "startTime": 222.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 225.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "個性の強い三人だからな\n年上でもこの三人をまとめるのは大変だと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 228.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
